<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>The cavalier is one of the most frecuent 'named' spawns in the lower tower in lguk, or dead tower as some call it. from the savant's room you go down the stairs and to the left till you reach wall then left again and he spawns in the farthers corner in the room, also 2 other frogs spawn there. he's lvl38 if im not wrong, hits pretty hard, 96 max if im not wrong and drops adamantite epolets (ac9 +7 wis) or dark reaver, a sk only 2hs weapon, forgot name..</font></td></tr></table>
