<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Jane</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-09-14 14:04:49</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Wisdom is good for tanks like SK's and Warriors for Mob's that cast mind type spells.. Like EE's who make pets outta players (heh or Negotiator in MM) and shammys who cast crap like walking sleep (not like the effect lasts long anyways). Wisdom helps you resist these type of spells, its not a major stat by a long shot for these classes tho, they would be much better off focused on another stat like Str or Dex.<BR>
<BR>
So yeah by itself Wis is more than useless to these tank classes,its a waste of an inventory slot much better filled by Str Dex or Agil gear.<BR>
<BR>
Anyways, hope this info helps.<BR>
<BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
